title: Crime Alert 04.18.19
itunes:title: Crime Alert 04.18.19
description:
Police say the arrest of serial killer has yielded "promising" leads on a number of unsolved murders of men in the Toronto area. New Hampshire Investigators renewed their search for 21-year-old college student, Maura Murray. Ohio death row inmate, Jason Dean, dies in prison from apparent natural causes.
